headline: TC Energy Q3 Earnings Match Estimates, Revenues Beat, Both Fall Y/Y
summary: TRP anticipates its 2025 comparable EBITDA to be between C$10.8 billion and C$11 billion, with net Capex to be between C$5.5 billion and C$6 billion.

headline: Northern Q3 Earnings Beat Estimates, Revenues Miss, Both Down Y/Y
summary: NOG expects total production of 132,500-134,000 barrels of oil equivalent per day, with oil production in the range of 75,000-76,500 barrels per day for 2025.

headline: Is There Now an Opportunity in Valero After 42.6% Share Price Surge in 2025?
summary: If you have ever wondered whether Valero Energy is a value play or just another hot stock, you are in exactly the right place. Valero’s stock price has surged recently, gaining 3.6% in the last week, 11.1% over the past month, and 42.6% year-to-date. This points to major momentum and shifting market sentiment.
